{"tid":1650621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[十八區開花] 低成本全民牆紙師","createTime":"2019-10-13T05:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T15:22:55.000Z","uid":187796,"like":347,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"07dbbd6b203057fe8dd219be633b73f943bd1055","tid":1650621,"uid":187796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:14:56.000Z","msg":"裝修好暴力所以要停？錯！<br />\n大家可以睇一睇呢張圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K7db6c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK7db6c8.jpg&h=54f2eceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[/red][/size=6]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暴力？邊忽暴力呀？睇過？</span></span><br />\n裝修係絕對可以<span style=\"color: gold;\">突顯我地冇無差別攻擊，良好公民質素</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢點呀！我地要做嘅唔係停止裝修，而係有<span style=\"color: red;\">針對性</span>，有足夠<span style=\"color: red;\">理由</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">護航</span>嘅情況下裝佢老味呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以今日開花，人人都係牆紙師，每個都同我印啲護航落街裝完貼滿佢，同全世界講呢啲垃圾點解會比人裝修。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">極低成本做法：<br />\n帶幾張廢紙，一支marker，一卷膠紙<br />\n[red]即裝 即寫 即貼 走人<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g0KVOrx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg0KVOrx.jpg&h=a47c45dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[size=6]<span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣靚唔靚唔緊要 你貼得係個原本傳媒會影嘅地方 無論佢靚唔靚都有人睇 最緊要多人貼</span></span><br />\n延伸閱讀：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P3T7EyC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP3T7EyC.jpg&h=75abbd2c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9CMdz60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9CMdz60.jpg&h=27355e99&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KtfejyK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKtfejyK.jpg&h=29aca2c8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yZf2tr8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyZf2tr8.jpg&h=e2e414c6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Btbdz7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBtbdz7d.jpg&h=54da90b0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EzUVOsf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEzUVOsf.jpg&h=94c7079c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ztQJXkC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FztQJXkC.jpg&h=577580d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ea0ac69f7cee48c10433a9dbc7b2a7e2803597f","tid":1650621,"uid":187796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:15:16.000Z","msg":"全民牆紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7421db3962f4f284565a79b8f07a81d98c87d38c","tid":1650621,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:15:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"00abbea8bda4c20ac1d66f0784e7633198688622","tid":1650621,"uid":187796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:15:44.000Z","msg":"全民牆紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66483bd8875ad79f16333089e06b73862d6c0cc","tid":1650621,"uid":70897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"Important"},{"pid":"8184a1e93a071c289cb09242203241bd635c48a3","tid":1650621,"uid":187796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:16:12.000Z","msg":"全民牆紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f48484a1670f06e8368f91de466865237df7850","tid":1650621,"uid":187796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:16:56.000Z","msg":"全民牆