d;\">針對性</span>，有足夠<span style=\"color: red;\">理由</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">護航</span>嘅情況下裝佢老味呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以今日開花，人人都係牆紙師，每個都同我印啲護航落街裝完貼滿佢，同全世界講呢啲垃圾點解會比人裝修。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">極低成本做法：<br />\n帶幾張廢紙，一支marker，一卷膠紙<br />\n[red]即裝 即寫 即貼 走人<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g0KVOrx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg0KVOrx.jpg&h=a47c45dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[size=6]<span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣靚唔靚唔緊要 你貼得係個原本傳媒會影嘅地方 無論佢靚唔靚都有人睇 最緊要多人貼</span></span><br />\n延伸閱讀：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P3T7EyC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP3T7EyC.jpg&h=75abbd2c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9CMdz60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9CMdz60.jpg&h=27355e99&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KtfejyK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKtfejyK.jpg&h=29aca2c8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yZf2tr8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyZf2tr8.jpg&h=e2e414c6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Btbdz7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBtbdz7d.jpg&h=54da90b0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EzUVOsf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEzUVOsf.jpg&h=94c7079c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ztQJXkC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FztQJXkC.jpg&h=577580d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kaPe4qz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkaPe4qz.jpg&h=e3961b3d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"855a2a48540c57f888afefa25933cf13a8cc62e6"